About

La Cruche was formed in 2020 between 10 friends eager to make the most of our shared passion for golf. It would be remiss to say that La Cruche isn't competitive, but it certainly isn't all about taking our beloved trophy home.

During a relaxation in COVID restrictions, the founding 8 members of La Cruche seized the opportunity to embark on our first Tour, Northern Ireland. Read all about the Northern Ireland Tour here.
